          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有座。可恼吓，可恼吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟这般嗔怒，与哪个淘气？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你妈儿娘淘气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与她淘的何气？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨日妈儿娘寿诞之日，为弟前去拜寿。满满斟上一杯酒，跪在她的面前，叫她"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "允承我一件大事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么大事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不叫姐姐迎宾接客。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她可曾允承？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她竟然不允。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她不允就罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她罢我不罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不罢，心想怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我心想告她。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你告她下何句语？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我告她买良为娼，私买人口。大老爷闻听此言，将她一顿板子打死，方消为弟"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心头之恨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟这两句话，还是你心中就有，还是旁人教道于你？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐说哪里话来，为弟长成一十六岁，这两句话，不会讲它，怎样为人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐告便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请便。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周翠屏背供。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观看陈魁，虽则年幼，说两句话，倒是个志气男子。我不免借他几百两银子，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫他大小做个买卖，日后若有发达，好将奴家救出娼门。就是这个主意。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周翠屏坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟你与她呈讼到官，岂不被旁人耻笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依姐姐之见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大小做个买卖才好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问姐姐：为弟要做什么买卖才好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟愿意做脸朝里的买卖，还是脸朝外的买卖？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脸朝里的怎讲，脸朝外的买卖怎说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脸朝里的买卖：身背货箱，东家门进，西家门出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脸朝外的买卖呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脸朝外的买卖：在这郓城县下，开一座绒线铺面，这就是脸朝外的买卖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脸朝外的买卖好做，也得三头五百两银子，为弟哪有许多银子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就该在大户人家去借。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐你又来了。为弟来在这郓城县，靠亲无亲，靠故无故，哪里去寻，哪里去"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "借？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢。你若肯满满斟上一杯酒，跪在我的面前，叫我三声“亲亲姐姐”，我就"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "借与你五百两银子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐真心？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "满满斟上一杯酒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "双膝跪在地留平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲亲姐姐，请来用酒，请来用酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟，你这算何意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟贺的是五百两银子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，怎么你就贺的那五百两银子么？我说兄弟吓，兄弟，想姐姐那五百两银子，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非从容易而来的吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一句话儿错出唇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见兄弟跪在地埃尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姐姐言来听原因："
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哪知姐姐费尽心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "后门送出无钱人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "难得积攒这五百银。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姐姐才的放下心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "用手儿搀起结拜弟"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "五百银子是小事"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "前门接了有钱客"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "命苦身落烟花巷"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但愿得买卖多茂盛"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姐姐不要两泪淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为弟也非无义人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我情愿将姐姐救出娼门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但愿买卖多茂盛"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿买卖多茂盛"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "救不救，全在你，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此话在心莫出唇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古路遥知马壮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "日久才见人的心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好一个路遥知马壮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "日久才见人的心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周翠屏开箱。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "亲手儿递你五百银。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见银两放桌案，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "再叫姐姐你听原因。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐，想为弟带了许多银两，若被你妈儿娘看见，她说为弟盗你的家财不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢，待姐姐去到楼上，缝上一条搭膊，将银两带出院去，瞒过妈儿娘，岂不"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭姐姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周翠屏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随姐姐上楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周翠屏、陈魁同上楼。小梆子。周翠屏捻线。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上楼来我这里打开针织，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "观兄弟容貌儿可算第一。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他哪知陈三两一片心机。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（行弦。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周翠屏 （花梆子原板） 叫兄弟你醒来细听仔细。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈魁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，兄弟苏醒，兄弟醒来。睡死你了！"
